_sText: Aim_ag_radical_textured ----------- 12 players or less (preferred) Description: The skill map aim_ag_radical retextured to be realistic to a certain extent. I like this map a lot and therefore decided to texture it for fun (and my own practise). Just thought why not share it in the process :) Objective: Use the objects and environment to beat your enemies in gunfights. Pure skill will save you from getting that one headshot you didn't deserve. Notes: HDR is included but possibly not optimal Nav file is not included but might still come. Autonav will suffice for this smaller map. Thanks and have fun if you download this :)
